---
title: Asian Sugar Snap Pea & Mint Slaw with Roasted Peanuts | Serves 2
description: This colourful Asian-style slaw is all about texture and flavour. We've added all the crunch to our ready-to-go slaw mix, with sugar snap peas and roasted peanuts.
